content: First and foremost, we remain committed to: one, our shareholders to be prudent, disciplined with every dollar we deploy; two, our customers to help them get back on the road with quality products at competitive prices; three, our team to invest in their safety, growth and personal development to ensure they have the tools and support they need to succeed and truly feel like owners in our business; four, last but not least our vendors, partners, communities and everyone who has been an integral part of the CarParts.com ecosystem for the last 25 years.
